        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Kang Na-Eon (Kim Ji-Eun) has worked her way up as a team leader at Seongsu Agency. She is a workaholic and will do anything to achieve success. She has also made plenty of enemies along the way. Kang Na-Eon is able to land an exclusive marketing contract with XU Cosmetics that could soon elevate her to an executive level position at Seongsu Agency's parent company Segye Group. Meanwhile, So Eun-Ho (Lomon) is an intern at Seongsu Agency. He can be goofy and naive at times, but his heart is sincere. During the course of his work, he takes up the side of handmade shoemakers, who must vacate their building to allow for a XU Cosmetics popup store. As Kang Na-Eon and So Eun-Ho butt heads over their ideals, a sinister case leads them to trade places.",
